   * build system was made useful (added autoconf, rewrote Makefile)
   * fixed numerical attribute parsing
   * fixed comment-in-quotes interpretation
   * added [else] system directive
   * removed rendered documentation from package (still available on website)
      * (hmm..  added autoconf _and_ reduced package size.  these are strange
         times indeed.)

